Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:01:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天突然要去店里帮忙 不能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...我要和小水她们去吃蛋糕自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起的时候 就说没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不愿意我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近只能买水果牛奶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,250)\1c&H6A00D5&}小\N水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去吃蛋糕自助餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕自助餐? 啊 上星期吃过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七没有去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说没钱 很羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们下次一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你去哪里 竹内已经先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着就知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.01,0:02:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在盯梢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 竹内一定知道矢野的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能陪我去买礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是高桥买的 不管什么他都会喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这么说 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥一个人挑的礼物一定更能让矢野喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我的眼光不是很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 高桥从矢野那里收到的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野的朋友挑的合乎高桥口味的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他花心思挑选但不合你口味的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个更让你开心?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 当然是矢野一个人选的更好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是买礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 明明没有钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要去店里帮忙了 没和我一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是年末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是我多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 出来了 出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着个袋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次盯梢圆满完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心你有没有买好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 买好啦 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都来了 一起喝个茶好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我还有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从匡那里听说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年出车祸的那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是你的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说你一次都没有去上过坟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为她 为你自己也应该去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买一束她喜欢的花 带上水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一趟吧 元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也应该哭一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个蠢女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢女人也会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算后悔 也太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\1c&000000&}9:30~10:00大扫除 扫雪\N10:30 结业式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 男生 认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打雪仗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有完没完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天矢野都没有正眼瞧过我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多心了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...多心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗绷着个脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不好玩啦 别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我还不了解矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圣诞礼物啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 因为我们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挑了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过喜欢帽子之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有毛绒绒的那种帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 颜色挑了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不过 如果你不喜欢我拿去换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\1c&H6A00D5&}非常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了呗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有礼物给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只能暂时喝水果牛奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是哭啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是感情丰富哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然别人说只能在悲伤的时候哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得高兴的眼泪比悲伤的眼泪要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识矢野之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像变得特别爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 数1的教材好像忘在柜子里没拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回去拿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 里面有一堆作业要写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回我跌下楼梯那次...多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不要再帮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢欠别人人情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然那么讨厌我 一开始就不该接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明是你为了向我姐姐报仇在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报仇?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事没有理由 也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把那件事加上特别的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么哭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 你为什么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了? 矢野哭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来有这回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 你为什么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候...是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 还是在山本面前 究竟是什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 寒假还把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我也有些在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不敢相信 他居然哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识他很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见他哭过 也从未见他露出过怯懦的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前你也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是人 都会有不为人知的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可矢野不是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 初中时山本和矢野之间发生过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时候觉得他们之间不是很自然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会呀 不是很正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本原本就是那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系不自然可能还是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少和奈奈有点关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈 为什么在前男友的车上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做背叛矢野的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她前男友很有魅力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男的很差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会和那种男人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还经常被打得浑身乌青
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌青 为什么和那种男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野也是 为什么和那种笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么质问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只有当事者自己知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那么冷把你叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和矢野也真是一对笨蛋情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是慌慌张张 连累别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笨蛋的情侣 我觉得不是真正的情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人刚开始交往的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有过"为什么和那种笨女人在一起"的疑问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很生气 像个笨蛋 跟白痴一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又不能不管他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是第一排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座位太不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是最糟糕的组合了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新座位真是太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后不能忘带东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 如果你没带教科书可以问我借
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以和同桌合看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有如果我睡着了 你要在她告状前叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个...太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 和山本做同桌 已经是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中二年级以来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候她也不借教科书给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我一次都没有忘带书
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(540,250)\1c&000000&}初\N中\N的\N时\N候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(380,220)\1c&000000&}他\N和\N山\N本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(200,360)\1c&000000&}究\N竟\N发\N生\N过\N什\N么\N?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要事情一和奈奈有关系 我就变得胆小起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次和竹内约好一起买圣诞礼物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么骗我说和小水去吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你? 我想给你个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然知道 但不许再骗我和别的男生一起出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隐瞒任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我 永远不背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天上第几页
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预习过了吗 借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在山本旁边很难受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次还被她瞪过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问她借看教科书 根本开不了口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想快点换座位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不清楚 你放中间好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻到45页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么预习了10页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家没事可干
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.60,0:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事干就学习?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\1c&000000&}自习中\N请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说没有梦想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想我可是有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有很多钱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以去迪斯尼乐园约会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你呢 有钱的话想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我? 我不要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要钱 不过想要爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的 居然第一个就要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 当然是爱更加重要咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 没关系 你要爱的话多少我都可以给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么星期六我父母不在 来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来矢野说的爱是上床...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\1c&H7D024D&\move(600,140,600,50)}呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 这样的话 星期六去我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父母不在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脑袋里成天就想着这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法答应你的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我内心很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩不玩?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没有钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的全部财产
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要矢野笑就可以了 那件事不问清楚也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望矢野可以一直笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没带生物书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得带回家一次就忘了带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我借你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看 山本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没什么 Byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好山本借你看课本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 星期天来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天的话 也许就不会不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母要出门?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里很小
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(300,0)}骗你什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间比你的小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把包放那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野在我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有些...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家住在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这里很远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算很远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和矢野在聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很帅哦 一定女孩缘很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(870,40,10,40)\1c&H4754EB&\3c&H00FFFF&}母亲 鉴定中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令尊在哪里高就呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越觉得对矢野很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爸爸从事不动产方面的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野家很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 你什么时候去过他家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家并不像看上去那样大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有进去过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间只有四叠半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放CD听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要听什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 随便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和在外面不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来打破这沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不会做的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你妈妈看上去是那种不敲门就进来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒茶来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好 宝贝你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我真的非常非常喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从和你交往之后 发现了好多你不为人知的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如...比如...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比我想的还要白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样抚摸我的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越来越喜欢矢野了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实...很妒嫉山本
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她知道我不了解的矢野的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.91,0:22:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做和矢野最亲近的人 我想了解矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都想了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很任性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.04,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次说过不能隐瞒任何事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后再也不会说谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以矢野也不要说谎好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.04,0:22:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只是多心 我也想问清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和山本之间发生过什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.83,0:22:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一样 因为感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了不隐瞒任何事的么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 不回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.42,0:25:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本喜欢过矢野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.99,0:25:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她喜欢还是讨厌我 都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.51,0:25:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我没关系 也没兴趣知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.04,0:25:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了 那天你们一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要去碰她妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.71,0:25:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我身边来 高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.14,0:25:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的

